---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Grownetics OS — AI Operations for Commercial Cultivation | Coming H2 2026"
  description="The AI operations layer for commercial CEA — connecting environment, people, and decisions into one system that compounds with every grow. Join the waitlist for first access."
  canonical="/os"
  bodyClass="os-page"
>

  <style>
    .os-page {
      --bg: #0D0C0A;
      --bg-alt: #141210;
      --surface: #1A1816;
      --text: #E8DDD0;
      --text-2: #C8BDB0;
      --text-3: #9A9080;
      --text-muted: #6A6055;
      --border: #2A2620;
      --green: #4E9E6A;
      --gold: #B89254;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    .cursor-blink {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 2px;
      height: 1em;
      background: #4E9E6A;
      vertical-align: text-bottom;
      margin-left: 2px;
      animation: blink 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .os-form-input {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(184,146,84,0.2);
      color: #E8DDD0;
      caret-color: #4E9E6A;
      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
    }
    .os-form-input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgba(78,158,106,0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(78,158,106,0.08);
    }
    .os-form-input::placeholder { color: rgba(154,144,128,0.5); }
    .os-form-input option { background: #1A1816; color: #E8DDD0; }
  </style>

  <script>
    // Swap nav logo to white for this dark page
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const logo = document.querySelector('nav img[alt="Grownetics"]') as HTMLImageElement | null;
      if (logo) logo.src = '/images/logo-white.png';
      const nav = document.getElementById('main-nav');
      if (nav) {
        nav.style.setProperty('--nav-text', '#E8DDD0');
      }
    });
  </script>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       FULL-PAGE HERO — ONE SCROLL, MAXIMUM DRAMA
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
    style="background: #0D0C0A;"
    aria-labelledby="os-headline"
  >
    <!-- Grid -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(184,146,84,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(184,146,84,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 72px 72px;"></div>
    <!-- Green glow — bottom left -->
    <div class="absolute pointer-events-none" style="bottom: -150px; left: -150px; width: 700px; height: 700px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(78,158,106,0.09) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <!-- Gold glow — top right -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 pointer-events-none" style="width: 500px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(184,146,84,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

    <!-- Catalog header bar -->
    <div class="absolute left-0 right-0" style="top: 64px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,146,84,0.1); padding: 10px 0; z-index: 10;">
      <div class="container flex items-center justify-between">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.4);">
          GROWNETICS FIELD CATALOG · VOL. II · RESTRICTED ACCESS
        </span>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(78,158,106,0.5);">
          STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT ◉
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container relative z-10 py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">

        <!-- Section ref -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
          <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.4))"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.5);">§ 001 · Coming H2 2026</span>
          <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.4))"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Status badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1.5 rounded border" style="color: rgba(78,158,106,0.8); border-color: rgba(78,158,106,0.25); background: rgba(78,158,106,0.06);">◉ In Development</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1.5 rounded border" style="color: rgba(232,221,208,0.3); border-color: rgba(232,221,208,0.1);">Early Access Opening</span>
        </div>

        <!-- THE HEADLINE — sparse, weighted -->
        <h1
          id="os-headline"
          class="font-display font-bold mb-4"
          style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: #E8DDD0;"
        >
          Intelligence is coming<br />
          <span style="color: #4E9E6A;">to the grow room.</span>
          <span class="cursor-blink" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Three sparse paragraphs — every word earns its place -->
        <div class="mt-10 mb-12 text-left max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-5">
          <p style="color: rgba(154,144,128,0.9); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Grownetics OS is the AI operations layer for commercial cultivation — the thing
            that connects your environment, your people, and your decisions into one system
            that gets smarter with every grow.
          </p>
          <p style="color: rgba(106,96,85,0.85); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            It is not monitoring software. It is not an ERP. It is not another dashboard.
            It is the operating system your facility has been running without.
          </p>
          <p style="color: rgba(106,96,85,0.7); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            We're bringing it to a small group of commercial operators first.
            If that's you, leave your email.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 justify-center">
          <div class="h-px flex-1 max-w-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.3))"></div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.4);">WAITLIST</span>
          <div class="h-px flex-1 max-w-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.3))"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Form — 2 fields only per Maven spec -->
        <form
          action="https://grownetics.com/forms/os-waitlist"
          method="POST"
          class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-3"
          aria-label="Join the Grownetics OS waitlist"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form" value="os-waitlist" />

          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Work email"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
            class="os-form-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded font-mono text-sm"
          />

          <select
            name="facility_size"
            class="os-form-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded font-mono text-sm"
            aria-label="Facility size"
          >
            <option value="">Facility size (canopy sq ft)</option>
            <option value="under-10k">Under 10,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="10k-50k">10,000 – 50,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="50k-200k">50,000 – 200,000 sq ft</option>
            <option value="200k-plus">200,000+ sq ft</option>
          </select>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn w-full justify-center py-3.5 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-white"
            style="background: #4E9E6A; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(78,158,106,0.25);"
          >
            Join the Waitlist → First Access
          </button>
        </form>

        <!-- Trust line -->
        <p class="font-mono text-xs mt-5" style="color: rgba(106,96,85,0.6);">
          No pitch. No timeline promises. When it's ready, you'll be first.
        </p>

        <!-- Back to main site -->
        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/" class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.4); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;"
             onmouseover="this.style.color='rgba(184,146,84,0.7)'"
             onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(184,146,84,0.4)'">
            ← Back to Grownetics
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       § 002 — THREE CAPABILITIES (sparse preview)
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section style="background: #141210; padding: 96px 0;" aria-label="Platform preview">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-14">
        <div class="w-0.5 h-3.5 rounded" style="background: rgba(184,146,84,0.5)"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.5);">§ 002 · Three Problems. One Operating System.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            ref: "A",
            name: "Unified Intelligence",
            body: "Query your entire facility history in natural language. Ask what your yield looked like six cycles ago when VPD was in range versus when it wasn't. Get an answer in seconds.",
            icon: "◈",
          },
          {
            ref: "B",
            name: "Predictive Operations",
            body: "Grownetics OS doesn't just report what happened — it anticipates what's about to happen. Catch drift before it costs you a harvest. Act on a recommendation, not a post-mortem.",
            icon: "◎",
          },
          {
            ref: "C",
            name: "Codified Expertise",
            body: "Your best cultivation decisions, captured, referenced, and applied at scale. The knowledge that walks out the door with your head grower — stays.",
            icon: "◇",
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div
            class="p-7 rounded-lg"
            style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.022); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.055);"
          >
            <div class="font-mono text-4xl mb-5" style="color: rgba(78,158,106,0.25);">{item.icon}</div>
            <div class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.45);">
              Capability · {item.ref}
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #E8DDD0;">{item.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(154,144,128,0.8);">{item.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       SECOND FORM — Final CTA
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section style="background: #0D0C0A; padding: 96px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;" aria-label="Join waitlist">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 pointer-events-none" style="height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom center, rgba(78,158,106,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

    <div class="container relative z-10 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto">

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.3))"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(184,146,84,0.45);">§ 003 · Access</span>
        <div class="h-px w-12" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, rgba(184,146,84,0.3))"></div>
      </div>

      <h2
        class="font-display font-bold mb-3"
        style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); color: #E8DDD0; line-height: 1.2;"
      >
        The waitlist is open.<br />
        <span style="color: #4E9E6A;">Early access is limited.</span>
      </h2>

      <p
        class="font-display italic mb-10"
        style="color: rgba(154,144,128,0.6); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6;"
      >
        Early access facilities will shape how Grownetics OS is built.
        Their data informs the model. Their feedback defines the roadmap.
      </p>

      <form
        action="https://grownetics.com/forms/os-waitlist"
        method="POST"
        class="space-y-3"
        aria-label="Join the Grownetics OS waitlist"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form" value="os-waitlist-bottom" />
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Work email"
            required
            autocomplete="email"
            class="os-form-input flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded font-mono text-sm"
          />
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-white flex-shrink-0"
            style="background: #4E9E6A;"
          >
            Join the Waitlist
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <p class="font-mono text-xs mt-5">
        <span style="color: rgba(106,96,85,0.6);">Already have Grownetics hardware? </span>
        <a href="/contact" style="color: rgba(78,158,106,0.65); text-decoration: underline;">
          You're already in line.
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
